<p>Sunday 1/7/17<br/>Church parade took charge &ndash; Scheme without troops with Hamilton towards Fremicourt.<br/>Monday 2/7/17<br/>Received news of the General being killed, saw Basil arranged to go up by car for funeral.<br/>Tuesday 3/7/17<br/>Left by car for Steenwerke, Bas, Wisdom, &amp; Watson. Funeral at 3 pm. General killed by shell fire at The Shrine near Messines, buried at Trois Arbres [Belgium] near Steenwerke with full military honrs, stayed night at 4th Div.</p>
